to put away perfection?

266
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:17,640
Ooh!
Ooh!Ooh!
Ooh!

267
00:12:21,430 --> 00:12:24,520
Rainbow Dash,
are you okay?

268
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,020
