in the best young fliers
competition.

273
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,530
Hey, there's an idea --

274
00:12:36,570 --> 00:12:38,530
You should enter
the competition.

275
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:39,370
Yeah.

276
00:12:39,370 --> 00:12:42,410
I could watch you fly
all day long.

277
00:12:42,450 --> 00:12:44,370
There really isn't anypony

278
00:12:44,410 --> 00:12:46,920
who uses their wings
quite like me.

279
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,460
Perhaps I should compete.

280
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:49,710
What?!

281
00:12:49,710 --> 00:12:52,210
Oooh!
Oooh!Oooh!
Oooh!

282
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:53,470
That's amazing!

283
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:56,220
Wow!
Ooh!

284
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:58,600
What am I gonna do?

285
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:01,180
I'll never win
the competition now.

286
00:13:17,990 --> 00:13:20,700
